{"tid":1993912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[推到完場] 請大家留意返尋日呢一個聲明書","createTime":"2020-04-29T06:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T06:02:11.000Z","uid":41846,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49f35486bbb4de90de4af2a8d45baf48964b7198","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"自由之地有限，中共之慾無厭 議會戰線立場聲明書<br />\n<br />\n自中共高調干預內會主席選舉程序，議會抗爭形勢波譎雲詭。中共步步進迫，宣稱郭榮鏗違反誓言，意欲取消其議員資格。<br />\n<br />\n內會主席選舉之重，在於癱瘓不公的內會會議，乃當下議會戰線的關鍵一仗。民主陣營歷經多年紛爭，可團結合作如此，實屬難能可貴之事。唯今晨明報刊出政情專欄，以「泛民內會『鬆手』會議加快 『解結』兩派仍互推波」為題，當中竟然有不具名泛民議員指，目前目標在於尋找下台階，讓步結束主席選舉程序。<br />\n<br />\n眼下面對港共政權步步進逼，香港民主陣營理應寸土必爭，於各戰線團結起來奮力抵抗。我們一眾議員難掩失望。正當我們集中精力深耕社區，鼓勵市民登記選民，在來屆立法會選舉中合眾人之力奪取議會過半之時，竟然從新聞上看見此示弱之舉。如此行事，得35+亦無所用。<br />\n<br />\n香港存亡繫於今秋，民主陣營不容內鬥。為此，我們一眾議員均全力配合協調，唯望能成大事。然而，任誰均不能繼續曖昧下去，香港已經沒有曖昧的空間。蘇洵之《六國論》有云：「今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。」不論放風者是誰，倘若泛民議員能澄清從無如此念頭，當能穩定民心。否則今日退讓一時，只會為中共及其爪牙積威，「日削月割，以趨於亡。」<br />\n<br />\n自由之地有限，中共之慾無厭；議會團結抗爭，寸土不容有失。<br />\n倘若我們仍不團結一致，即使35+成功，亦只會淪為戀棧權力的「忠誠反對派」，辜負一直為此目標努力、犧牲的同路人。<br />\n<br />\n還請在議會內的代議士盡快以行動回應，顯示決心，否則難以信服大眾如何對體制內抗爭保持信心。<br />\n<br />\n聯署名單：因為不停更新，我唔貼呢度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tg34y6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftg34y6p.jpg&h=d5de0e70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"062c51495f8ae5bc1cff27a2c6d5b1fb3a88d49c","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5e031fe93eb3a92ec04b8aac04adc94fa3f0a18","tid":1993912,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48630a3f740de3a5f27663e014925e1ba7a8054e","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd0648865bc29c872f5d2c7a27be263cb95c60f1","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3461fe5a45c530bffb308db43ad4cfe5a45facb5","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6e19227825130db32dcd63e561233ce8ff0ae79","tid":1993912,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a533c7c200851dcbb696521aefbf3ae2ef6b1e2b","tid":1993912,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"pishh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6398d455de576d2038ef9e0ccf96592806b8fdb1","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"cd1f2162e209eed5f6fb0e6bc316da65f12cb913","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"54b8b38ff1cb929b96ddd5330753a268d06f00f5","tid":1993912,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30